-- Air France Seeks 4,390 Staff Departures by March 2013, La Tribune Reports
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-06-24T04:18:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/air-france-seeks-4-390-staff-departures-by-march-2013-la-tribune-reports.html

          
          
             Air France is seeking 4,390 staff
departures by March 2013, La Tribune reported, citing a planning
document to be presented by management to unions in July.  
 The departures will be voluntary and the total excludes
non-French units of Air France-KLM Group SA, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        